      <h2 class="section__heading">The monthly bookkeeping checklist.</h2>
      <p class="section__lede">Seven steps, in order. Run them the same way every month &mdash; if you hit a step the file won&rsquo;t pass, like an account that won&rsquo;t reconcile, stop and get the file reviewed before it compounds.</p>
    </header>
    <ol class="fix-steps">
